TestDiscoverHandlesIcelandicGoalNames
/ Discovery must be encoding-safe for non-ASCII filenames and goal names.
/ The fixture directory contains a Próf.fixture.goal with goal name "Próf".
/ Assert discover finds it and carries the Icelandic name on EntryGoalName.
- test.discover tests in '_fixtures' recursive, pattern='*.fixture.goal', write to %tests%
- list.count %tests%, write to %count%
- assert %count% equals 1
- list.any %tests% where EntryGoalName equals 'Próf', write to %hasProf%
- assert %hasProf% is true
